    "headerDoc": "STEP 911 — Fibonacci Prime Infinitude ★★★ (Rei 固有接続)\n  =========================================================\n\n  Fibonacci sequence: F_0 = 0, F_1 = 1, F_{n+2} = F_n + F_{n+1}.\n  Fibonacci prime: F_n itself prime.\n  Known Fibonacci prime indices: 3, 4, 5, 7, 11, 13, 17, 23, 29, 43,\n  47, 83, 131, 137, 359, 431, 433, 449, 509, 569, 571, 2971, 4723,\n  5387, 9311, 9677, 14431, 25561, 30757, 35999, 37511, 50833, 81839,\n  104911, ~34 known (as of 2024).\n\n  **Rei 固有接続**: Paper 698 (STEP 698) で **F_14 = 377** が\n  peak-9232 Collatz atomic core の first arithmetic predecessor と判明.\n  π(64) = 96 = Rei M"
